            <title><![CDATA[【又到过敏季！#我国100个人中约有40个会过敏#[吃惊] 】#为何过敏的人越来越多# ？北京世纪坛医院变态反应科主任王洪田介绍，过敏也叫“富贵病”，经济社会越发...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[【又到过敏季！<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E6%88%91%E5%9B%BD100%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E4%B8%AD%E7%BA%A6%E6%9C%8940%E4%B8%AA%E4%BC%9A%E8%BF%87%E6%95%8F%23&amp;extparam=%23%E6%88%91%E5%9B%BD100%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E4%B8%AD%E7%BA%A6%E6%9C%8940%E4%B8%AA%E4%BC%9A%E8%BF%87%E6%95%8F%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#我国100个人中约有40个会过敏#</span></a><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[吃惊]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_chijing-59b444adb6.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span> 】<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E4%B8%BA%E4%BD%95%E8%BF%87%E6%95%8F%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%BA%E8%B6%8A%E6%9D%A5%E8%B6%8A%E5%A4%9A%23&amp;extparam=%23%E4%B8%BA%E4%BD%95%E8%BF%87%E6%95%8F%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%BA%E8%B6%8A%E6%9D%A5%E8%B6%8A%E5%A4%9A%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#为何过敏的人越来越多#</span></a> ？北京世纪坛医院变态反应科主任王洪田介绍，过敏也叫“富贵病”，经济社会越发达，过敏患者就会越多。很多人过敏，会遗传给下一代，包括过敏性鼻炎、过敏性哮喘、过敏性皮肤病、过敏性胃肠炎等等。另外，抗生素滥用也是过敏患者增多的原因之一。抗生素用得越多，有益细菌就会越少，过敏就会越多，这就是过敏疾病的“卫生假说”。<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4872754571444281" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">央视网的微博视频</span></a><br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://wx1.sinaimg.cn/orj480/003z5L7fly8hbet8tcgyaj60zk0k0tad02.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://locallimit.us.sinaimg.cn/o0/cZ2fQqQIlx083p7d0AMU01041200NyJA0E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=1280x720.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1677446280&amp;ssig=vMYWwztJzD&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://locallimit.us.sinaimg.cn/o0/HBDSpFNplx083p7cg27K01041200oeTU0E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=852x480.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1677446280&amp;ssig=3FFWW5OMv%2F&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://locallimit.us.sinaimg.cn/o0/xoUSdvvAlx083p7bLUwU01041200fyxP0E010.mp4?label=mp4_ld&amp;template=640x360.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1677446280&amp;ssig=Acuzf3n7EE&amp;KID=unistore,video"><p>视频无法显示，请前往<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034%3A4872754571444281&amp;luicode=10000011&amp;lfid=1076032831150640" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">微博视频</a>观看。</p></video>]]></description>
