            <description><![CDATA[【<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E8%B6%8580%25%E5%A5%B3%E6%80%A7%E4%BC%9A%E6%84%9F%E6%9F%93HPV%E7%97%85%E6%AF%92%23&amp;extparam=%23%E8%B6%8580%25%E5%A5%B3%E6%80%A7%E4%BC%9A%E6%84%9F%E6%9F%93HPV%E7%97%85%E6%AF%92%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#超80%女性会感染HPV病毒#</span></a>】<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%2399%25%E4%BB%A5%E4%B8%8A%E7%9A%84%E5%AE%AB%E9%A2%88%E7%99%8C%E4%B8%8EHPV%E6%8C%81%E7%BB%AD%E6%84%9F%E6%9F%93%E6%9C%89%E5%85%B3%23&amp;extparam=%2399%25%E4%BB%A5%E4%B8%8A%E7%9A%84%E5%AE%AB%E9%A2%88%E7%99%8C%E4%B8%8EHPV%E6%8C%81%E7%BB%AD%E6%84%9F%E6%9F%93%E6%9C%89%E5%85%B3%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#99%以上的宫颈癌与HPV持续感染有关#</span></a>过去20年，宫颈癌发病率和死亡率呈逐年上升的趋势，且在逐渐年轻化，而我国适龄女孩HPV疫苗接种率不足1%。现在已经明确99%以上的宫颈癌都与HPV持续感染有关。HPV病毒主要通过直接接触传播和性活动传播，早婚、早育、多个性伴侣、吸烟等都是触发宫颈癌的危险因素，大众健康知识普及至关重要。<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4872675903078511" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">央视网的微博视频</span></a><br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://wx4.sinaimg.cn/orj480/003z5L7fly8hbek7kaunhj60zk0k0adv02.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://locallimit.us.sinaimg.cn/o0/LvQogRN0lx083oLINiPS01041200qPYn0E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=1280x720.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1677446280&amp;ssig=ocjiSNWYkG&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://locallimit.us.sinaimg.cn/o0/o1z4YpCGlx083oLIdPpe01041200dFKf0E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=852x480.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1677446280&amp;ssig=OBp4fmyytq&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://locallimit.us.sinaimg.cn/o0/af5TKiu8lx083oLHI92o010412008CGe0E010.mp4?label=mp4_ld&amp;template=640x360.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1677446280&amp;ssig=FpwWaLHE%2FU&amp;KID=unistore,video"><p>视频无法显示，请前往<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034%3A4872675903078511&amp;luicode=10000011&amp;lfid=1076032831150640" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">微博视频</a>观看。</p></video>]]></description>
